bf881a64-0fed-11ef-acf0-36ed3c6c91fc.description:
Enhance skincare rituals with this smoothing facial massager designed to sculpt the contours of the face, release tension, and awaken skin. Inspired by ancient beauty traditions, this revitalizing Gua Sha tool boosts product application by stimulating the look of collagen, reducing the appearance of puffiness, and promoting lymphatic drainage.

Directions: Prep freshly cleansed skin with an oil, serum, or moisturizer to allow for enhanced glide of the tool while maximizing formula efficacy. Maintaining a light pressure, glide in alternating strokes along the natural curves of the face, neck, and décolleté. After use, rinse any residue from the tool with warm water. Dry with a cloth prior to storing.

Use 2-3 times per week for up to 5 minutes. For a cooling effect, store in the refrigerator prior to use.

bf881de8-0fed-11ef-acf0-36ed3c6c91fc.description:
NEW! A powerful plant-based Vitamin C concentrate that targets dark spots for visible improvement of complexion, amplified radiance, and brighter skin.

The percentage in the product title signifies the strength of the concentrated dose of the active ingredient within our formulation. Our Vitamin C THDA Elixir utilizes a 20% strength Vitamin C -- Tetrahexyldecyl Ascorbate (THDA) – which is a lot more potent when compared to the average 15% strength inclusion of common Vitamin C ingredient, L-Ascorbic Acid. Non-irritating, oil-soluble THDA is the superior form of Vitamin C, as it is more powerful, stable, and biocompatible than its water-soluble, unstable counterpart.

Apply directly to targeted areas or blend to boost other products. Use AM + PM on freshly cleansed skin. For use as a targeted treatment, apply a generous layer directly to skin. To boost the efficacy of compatible products, blend a few drops in the palm of your hand to any of the following:

Seeds of Youth Serum
Jojoba Glow Face Oil
Activated Botanical Primer
Brightening Botanical Eye Balm
Indigo Dream Renewal Cream

bf882540-0fed-11ef-acf0-36ed3c6c91fc.title: Dynamic Duo

bf88255e-0fed-11ef-acf0-36ed3c6c91fc.description:
Perfect the appearance of no-makeup-makeup with this multi-use skin-loving stick, rich in a hydrating blend of essential fatty acids and oils. This lightweight, illuminizing formula utilizes Green Coffee Oil to stimulate collagen, Sal Tree Resin to refine the appearance of pores, and Organic Tapioca powder to smooth the appearance of skin and absorb excess oils. The sheer color and subtle shimmer allow for a buildable glow to accentuate and enliven natural features.

Apply our silky-smooth Activated Botanical Primer to create a flawless canvas for application. Apply directly to skin and glide onto cheeks, lip, brow bone, eyelids, or body to bronze, highlight, contour, and blush. Set the look with the Luminous Botanical Face Mist.

bf882586-0fed-11ef-acf0-36ed3c6c91fc.description:
NEW! Amplify the appearance of flawless, glowing skin with this multi-benefit, mineral pigment moisturizing stick.

The nourishing, buildable formula delivers pure mineral pigments to instantly even complexion and balance skin tone, while a powerful blend of Pracaxi Seed Oil and Patchouli Leaf Extract improve elasticity and collagen production for long-term results.

For best results, use multiple shades to mimic the natural tone variations of skin, or double as a contouring bronzer with a deeper shade.

bf8825a4-0fed-11ef-acf0-36ed3c6c91fc.description:
Effortlessly enhance the natural contours of the face with three easy-to-apply, balmy sticks. Each Contour Collection includes three crystal-inspired shades to bronze, blush, and highlight your way to our signature glow. 

Crystal Contour Collection:  Our best-selling and most versatile trio to achieve a no-makeup-makeup glow. Trace hollows of cheekbones with Copper for a radiant cocoa bronze. Tap a few dabs of Rose Quartz to the apples of cheeks for a rosy blush. Add a swipe of Opal to the tops of cheekbones for a starlit highlight.

Golden Contour Collection: The ultimate warm-toned trio to achieve luminous, glow-from-within skin. Trace hollows of cheekbones with Amber for a soft, sunkissed tan. Tap a few dabs of Topaz to the apples of cheeks for a warm, rosy peach blush. Add a swipe of Carnelian to the tops of cheekbones for a luminous coral highlight.

Radiant Contour Collection: The essential rosy-hued trio to amplify natural radiance with a soft flush. Trace hollows of cheekbones with Obsidian for a defined deep bronze. Tap a few dabs of Pink Diamond to the apples of cheeks for a neutral pink blush. Add a swipe of Pearl to the tops of cheekbones for a pearlescent peony glow.

bf88263a-0fed-11ef-acf0-36ed3c6c91fc.title: The Precision Brush

bf88264e-0fed-11ef-acf0-36ed3c6c91fc.description:
A powerful cleansing soap that effectively removes makeup and buildup from cosmetic brushes without harsh chemicals for a beyond-clean application.

Directions: Wet makeup brush with warm water and rub over the soap to create a lather. Gently scrub bristles while rinsing. Rinse brush thoroughly with warm water and repeat as needed. Hold brush downward whenever wet. Remove any excess water from brush. Let brush dry completely. Rinse and remove any excess water from cleansing soap jar. Let dry completely before capping. Recommended cleaning 2-3 times per week. 

Certified Organic • Cruelty-Free • Not Tested on Animals • Vegan • Gluten-Free • All Natural • GMO-Free • Made in USA
